
---

## 📁 `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Node modules
node_modules/

# Logs
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# System files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Cache
.cache/
dist/
build/

# Environment files (if used later)
.env
.env.local
.env.development.local
.env.test.local
.env.production.local

# VSCode settings
.vscode/
